ncorporating meter operator mop data collection and aggregation dcda services electricity connections meters and amr services for both fiscal and submetering applications ask us about our free water audit services water efficiently managing energy usage by taking control of local loads control our mission to be the leading provider of multiutility industrial  commercial ic metering and network services delivering efficiency innovation and value why work with us end to end it is our ability to deliver true ‘endtoend’ support for britain’s businesses and public service providers that sets us apart we design and manage energy utility networks upstream and downstream of the meter install advanced metering and collect and deliver energy consumption data through automated meter reading systems operational efficiency energy assets is one of britain’s leading and fastest growing independent metering businesses we help private and public sectors to improve their energy efficiency through groundbreaking technologies realtime data and innovative customer centric processes compliance everything we do is fully compliant with the relevant legislative and industry standards – supported by a robust internal and external audit regime industry expertise we have assembled a team of industry experts and we continue to invest in the development of our people to meet and exceed the needs of our customers   multiutility our multiutility service delivery across gas electricity and water provides customers with a bundled proposition from a trusted service provider from our accredited design team through to fiscal or submetering and compliance ready consumption data delivered to your desk energy assets service will reduce upfront costs enabling work to be carried out efficiently by one party view multiutility solutions   we’re leaders in our sector and have the evidence to prove it we work closely with our customers to provide multiutility network and metering services browse our case studie